    <h2>Definition List</h2>

    <p>
        A definition list is used to define terms and provide their descriptions.
    </p>

    <p>
        <em><b>Task:</b> Create a definition list to describe Internet Application Programming.</em>
    </p>

    <dl>

        <dt><b>Internet Application Programming</b></dt>
        <dd>
            The process of developing software applications that run on the internet using web technologies.
        </dd>

        <dt><b>HTML</b></dt>
        <dd>
            A markup language used to structure and organize content on web pages.
        </dd>

        <dt><b>CSS</b></dt>
        <dd>
            A style sheet language used to control the layout and appearance of web pages.
        </dd>

        <dt><b>JavaScript</b></dt>
        <dd>
            A programming language used to add interactivity and dynamic features to websites.
        </dd>

        <dt><b>Web Server</b></dt>
        <dd>
            A system that hosts websites and delivers web pages to users through the internet.
        </dd>

    </dl>

